{
    int max=Integer.MIN_VALUE;
    int second_max=Integer.MIN_VALUE;

    for(int i=0;i<n;i++)
    {
        if(nums[i]>max)
        {
            second_max=max;
            max=nums[i];
        }
        else if(nums[i]!=max&&nums[i]>second_max)
        {
            second_max=nums[i];
        }
    }
}


Note:

    This is the optiised approach find the second largest number present in an array.
    The approach used here is an greedy approach